text: Miss Thailand World 2019 is the 29th edition of the Miss Thailand World. Pageant will be held at The Berkeley Pratunam Hotel in Bangkok on August 3, 2019. Miss Thailand World 2018 and Miss World 2018 Runner-Up Nicolene Pichapa Limsnukan of Bangkok crowned Narintorn Chadapattarawalrachoat of Pathum Thani at the end of the event.
